{
  "stem": "3848.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He took me down that transport, because the transport was going towards Italy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went with him to this camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In order for this particular camp, Bindermichl, it's a DP camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was supported by UNRRA, American UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this particular camp was-- Bindermichl was organized right after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The concentration survivors-- concentration camp survivors-- went to that place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They took over a lot of buildings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They decided that all the concentration camp people will meet over there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's where you're going to gather, Bindermichl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they established that camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In order to get into this camp, you had to be either a relative or somebody-- immediate family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Otherwise you can't sign in, because the camp was full.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When I came by, he was registered in that camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In order for me to get in there, I had to say that he is my brother.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I had to take his name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And instead of Tennenbojm or Gresores that I had on the road and other names, I became Gerald Grossman as a brother.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I lived there in this camp, registered in all Austria, in Linz, with a passport, till I left Europe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But in between, I had some other things that was happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was-- we had-- we didn't know that-- we had-- we knew we had relatives in the United States.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My grandmother lived in the United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was named after my grandfather that lived in the United States, came to Europe, and he died in Europe-- appendicitis.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So he never made it back to the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He only came for a visit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I'm named after him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "My grandmother died in New Jersey over here in 1941.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She lived in New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But she's buried in New Jersey.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
